{"type": "article", "id": 5920, "title": "《杀死一只知更鸟》50 年后", "description": "Best On The Web 是一个推荐性栏目，每个工作日我们会从互联网世界中找出最好看的内容，希望这个栏目让我们始终与阅读、知识和美好在一起。", "date": "2015-02-05T08:19:05Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [{"id": 6805, "name": "杀死一只知更鸟"}, {"id": 6806, "name": "Harper Lee"}, {"id": 456, "name": "文学"}, {"id": 6807, "name": "生命不能承受之轻"}, {"id": 6812, "name": "米兰·昆德拉"}], "category": 12, "author": 13, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071232081h7DvnSsRgtFY4da.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<strong>Latimes</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.latimes.com/books/jacketcopy/la-jc-harper-lee-to-to-kill-a-mockingbird-sequel-20150203-story.html?utm_source=nextdraft&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>\"To Kill a</strong><strong> Mockingbird\" Sequel \"Go Set a Watchman\"</strong></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t自完成《杀死一只知更鸟》之后，Harper Lee 似乎就在这个世界上消失了，以至于当 88 岁的她的新书 Go Set a Watchman 出来的时候，很多媒体都把这当成了「突发新闻」。不过即便如此，她也不愿意为了这本书公开露面。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123207cbPehZYJsFAIdHwq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7390625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t以《杀死一只知更鸟》中一幕场景为灵感的插画\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t这本新书显然是《杀死一只知更鸟》的续篇，预计在今年七月出版，起印 200 万册，同时会有电子版。新书其实比《杀死一只知更鸟》开始得更早。《杀死一只知更鸟》为她赢得了普利策奖，还被<strong><a href=\"http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0056592/\" target=\"_blank\">改编为电影</a></strong>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t同样有新书露面的是作家<strong><a href=\"http://www.theguardian.com/books/2015/feb/03/milan-kundera-new-novel-the-festival-of-insignificance?utm_source=nextdraft&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\">米兰·昆德拉，这也是他在过去十多年内出版的唯一一本英文小说</a></strong>。\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}